casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
Trevon Jaquan MCAFEE, Defendant-Appellee. SC: 157819
COA: 341612 Supreme Court of Michigan. September 12, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the March 28, 2018 order of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the question presented should be reviewed by this Court.
